                              <p><p style="text-align: left;">It’s so frustrating when rush hour spoils the perfectly planned back to back meetings. At Uber, our aim is to provide you with frictionless movement from one place to another. So we’ve made sure that you no longer have to worry about the math of travel timings.</p>
                              <br>
<h1>ALWAYS BE ON TIME USING THE LATEST UBER APP!</h1>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>To get zero click Ubers, you…</strong></p>
<ol>
<li>Allow Uber to access your calendar</li>
<li>Forget about transport and focus on your meetings</li>
<li>When Uber notifies you, swipe to order your Uber</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Oh and did we tell you that Uber detects who you are meeting with and your colleagues receive a text with a link to a live map that shows exactly when you’ll arrive at your destination!</strong></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-28833" alt="3phonecomp2" src="3phonecomp3.png" width="600" height="506" /></p>
<p>Sit back in your meetings, and forget about traffic. Use Zero Click Ubers for:</p>
<ul>
<li>The busy days when you’re meeting all your customers
</li>
<li>Making in time for your child’s soccer game
</li>
<li>That movie date after the gym</li>
</ul>
<p>It’s a simple formula: Uber + Calender =  Peace </p>
<p>Traffic is chaotic, Uber isn't.</p>
